</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Restaurant Industry Faces A Sudden Collapse In Coronavirus Shutdowns</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Rapid shutdowns to stem the coronavirus have delivered an unprecedented blow to restaurants around the U.S. Many are quickly running out of cash and their workers are losing their jobs.</b>
</div>
<div id="wrapper">
